se they had missed the first hundred over the several hours I was there), when it occurred to me that we must really suck.<br>
<br>
A shaman LFG means I solo.<br>
A rogue LFG means I solo.<br>
A war LFG means I solo.<br>
A cleric LFG means I solo.<br>
A ranger LFG means I solo.<br>
A Shadow Knight LFG means I solo.<br>
A paladin LFG means I solo.<br>
An enchanter LFG means I solo.<br>
A druid LFG will often mean I solo cause they can backup heal *and* nuke almost as well as a wiz.<br>
A mage LFG means I solo.<br>
A BL LFG means I solo.<br>
A necro LFG solos near me, but totally owns me.<br>
<br>
I truly believe we need serious help.<br>
