<br>
When I zone into PoV with my cleric, if I dont get a tell immediately (commonly I dont) I wait just as long as my wizard for a group. A zone can only support as many clerics as there are groups. 6 groups, 6 clerics max. 6 groups can support way more than 6 wizards. That's the counterbalance.<br>
<br>
