<br>
I have never had a problem finding a group when I want to, or building a group.  The only times I have is when there was really no one in the zone I was hoping to group in.<br>
<br>
I think to many people aren't aggressive enough in lfg or putting together a group.  If you see a half filled group, ask if you can join.  Most times people will say yes, if they are your lvl range.  If you /ooc, it is to easy for that group to just continue what they were doing before.<br>
<br>
With all the balancing effects put in to our class, and with the relative ease of having KEI, we are invaluable to most groups at least under 50.  I can almost chain cast Garrisons MM non-stop with KEI + Focus without drawing aggro or going LOM, and that is about 175dmg a pop.  And if we get adds, I can ghetto mez and burn down/kite adds.<br>
<br>
Maybe we should stop selling ourselves short in the community, and instead, post group strategies from time to time for other classes to see our strengths.<br>
