<br>
On the worst LFG of my night perhaps a week or so ago, I went 6 hours trying to find a group in PoV at level 61.  Fuck, I tried being witty, smart, whatever you wanna call it.  And the most goddamn insulting thing was that I saw this happen sooo many times:<br>
    A monk zones in, sais LFG, and is picked up within 5 minutes.<br>
   A shaman zones in, sais LFG, and is picked up within 5 minutes.<br>
   A rogue zones in and before he can say anything gets invites to half a dozen groups.<br>
   Rinse and repeat for most classes.<br>
<br>
The absolute truth is that although social skills can help you get a group if you play an &quot;undesired&quot; class, you are having to overcome class limitations through use of your social skills.<br>
<br>
Sure, you guys can sit back and say that *I* suck without having any information to back that up.  You can say that I have no personality.. I won't get into a debate on my social skills.. I think they are just fine, thank you.  <br>
<br>
I am just sick of LFG.  I personally feel like I am playing a different game than those of you that say you &quot;never&quot; have problems getting groups.<br>
<br>
Please note that I am talking about PoV in particular here.  If I go to PoN and group with a bunch of mid fifties, they are happy to have me PL them for a bit.<br>
<br>
Do I solo while LFG?  Yep.. I solo golems.  Do I like it?  Hell no.  <br>
<br>
I want to kill mobs that are level appropriate for me--that means killing in PoV or PoS at the moment.  <br>
<br>
** No class should be forced to solo level appropriate mobs  in a MMORPG. **<br>
<br>
To those that made baseless personal attacks against me, fuck you.  To those that responded intelligently but disagreed--thanks but we still disagree.  To those that agreed, well.. look me up on ARo--wizzies stack well and we can duo the golems sometime.<br>
